{"word":"ἀπόφασις 1","slug":"ἀπόφασις 1","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n14189\" key=\"a)po/fasis1\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">ἀπόφᾰσις</orth> (A), <itype lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"itype\">εως</itype>, <gen lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gen\">ἡ</gen>, (<etym lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"etym\">ἀπόφημι</etym>) <sense id=\"n14189.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">denial, negation,</tr_> opp. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">κατάφασις,</foreign> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0059.tlg007.perseus-grc1:263e\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pl.\">Pl.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Sph.\">Sph.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">263e</biblScope> </bibl>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἀ. ἐστιν ἀπόφανσίς τινος ἀπό τινος</foreign> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">a predication</tr_> of one thing <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">away from</tr_> another, i.e. <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">negation</tr_> of it, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0086.tlg017:17a:25\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Arist.\">Arist.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Int.\">Int.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">17a25</biblScope></bibl>, cf.<bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0086.tlg001:72a:14\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ APo.\">APo.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">72a14</biblScope> </bibl>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἀ. τινός</foreign> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">negation, exclusion</tr_> of a thing, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0059.tlg005.perseus-grc1:426d\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pl.\">Pl.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Cra.\">Cra.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">426d</biblScope> </bibl>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">δύο ἀ.</foreign> <pb n=\"226\" TEIform=\"pb\"/> <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">μίαν κατάφασιν ἀποτελοῦσι</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0062.tlg019:11\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Luc.\">Luc.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Gall.\">Gall.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">11</biblScope></bibl></cit>. </sense> <sense n=\"II\" id=\"n14189.1\" level=\"2\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">negative particle,</tr_> e.g. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">οὐ,</foreign> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0082.tlg002:124:8\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ A.D.\">A.D.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Adv.\">Adv.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">124.8</biblScope></bibl>, al.; <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">sign of negation,</tr_> <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Stoic.\">Stoic.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.52</biblScope> </bibl> (pl.).</sense> </entryFree>"}]}